title: Sword Emperor as son-in-law
description: Sword Emperor as son-in-law, 剑帝为婿 Sword Emperor as son-in-law : Emperor Nirvana reborn as a drunkard? Still reduced to a shameful son-in-law? However, the bride is the little girl who rescued him back then. In this life, I will become the strongest just to protect you! Emperor Nirvana reborn as a drunkard?
